        "c13717d6-5def-40f5-9684-68f8f103b0d4": {
          "type": "tab",
          "settings": {
            "column": "secondary",
            "title": "Shipping & Installation Information",
            "icon": "icon-check-circle-1",
            "icon_size": 2,
            "color_icon": "rgba(0,0,0,0)",
            "svg-code": "",
            "text": "<p>At Fenceworks, we do things a little differently — no surprise boxes dumped on your driveway. We offer white-glove installation to ensure your playset is expertly assembled and ready for play.</p><ul><li><strong>White-Glove Installation:</strong> If you’re within 60 miles of our Northbrook office, our team will handle delivery and installation with care. With 58+ years of experience and in-depth knowledge of city codes, we make sure everything is set up safely and correctly.</li><li><strong>Outside Our Service Area?</strong> If you’re beyond 60 miles, additional fees may apply. Please call us at <a href=\"tel:847-432-0900\" title=\"tel:847-432-0900\">847-432-0900</a> or email <a href=\"mailto:contact@theguyon41.com\" title=\"mailto:contact@theguyon41.com\">contact@theguyon41.com</a> to get a custom installation quote.</li><li><strong>DIY Installation:</strong> Prefer to handle the setup yourself? No problem — give us a call to coordinate a pickup from our Northbrook location.<br/><br/></li></ul><p><strong>Questions?</strong> Reach out anytime. We’re here to help every step of the way.</p>",
            "image_width": 1000,
            "align": "center",
            "link": "",
            "tab_content": "",
            "open": false
          }
        },
        "663a3435-b014-41e0-916d-1ed9505f5691": {
          "type": "tab",
          "settings": {
            "column": "secondary",
            "title": "Warranty & Fenceworks Guarantee",
            "icon": "icon-check-circle-1",
            "icon_size": 2,
            "color_icon": "rgba(0,0,0,0)",
            "svg-code": "",
            "text": "<p><em>We stand behind our playsets with a limited lifetime warranty — no fine print, no gimmicks. From natural wear and tear to unexpected surprises, we’ve got you covered. The only exceptions are acts of nature (like a tree falling) or intentional damage (like taking a baseball bat to the playground). Play hard with confidence — we’re here for the long haul. Contact </em><a href=\"mailto:contact@theguyon41.com\" title=\"mailto:contact@theguyon41.com\">contact@theguyon41.com</a> for support.</p>",
            "image_width": 1000,
            "align": "center",
