      "blocks": {
        "template--16580692508926__9904a28f-6381-41fe-96eb-d4a73d60f0a0-1666784019a14d8867-0": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "media": "quote",
            "svg-code": "",
            "image_round": true,
            "text": "<p>My old swing set broke just weeks before my son’s birthday party. I called Jake and within two weeks. I had a new swingset in my backyard. He made the entire process as easy as it could be.</p>",
            "name": "Rockne",
            "source": "Google Reviews"
          }
        },
        "template--16580692508926__9904a28f-6381-41fe-96eb-d4a73d60f0a0-1666784019a14d8867-1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "media": "quote",
            "svg-code": "",
            "image_round": true,
            "text": "<p>About 15 years ago, we purchased a swing set for our yard. Our kids and the neighborhood kids spent hours playing outside on it. Now that we are selling our home, we are leaving behind the set, and I have to believe that its presence in the yard helped the sale price. Truly a great long-term investment, that brought countless memories to our family.</p>",
            "name": "David",
            "source": "Google Reviews"
          }
        },
        "template--16580692508926__9904a28f-6381-41fe-96eb-d4a73d60f0a0-1666784019a14d8867-2": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "media": "quote",
            "svg-code": "",
            "image_round": true,
            "text": "<p>Fenceworks does amazing work!  Communication is transparent and respectful, and can see why they are a multigenerational family business and have been around for decades! No one does it better!</p>",
            "name": "Joey R.",
            "source": "Google"
          }
        }
      },
